0.1.0
  - Migrated to Resonance community plugin repository
  - Binaries no longer bundled; downloaded on-demand from philippe44/LMS-Raop
  - Cleaned up logging (use %s formatting instead of f-strings)
  - Plugin uses PluginContext.server_info for squeeze2raop server address
  - Tests adapted: ensure_binary mocked, platform-independent path assertions
  - Added plugin.toml manifest

0.0.1
  - Initial development by Pinoatrome
  - Moved to plugin framework
  - Added pytest suite
  - Added squeeze2raop configuration (XML parse/dump)
  - Added raopbridge plugin preferences (JSON settings)
  - Added squeeze2raop executable management
  - Added PID file and logging (category/levels)
  - Added GNU General Public License, version 2
  - Generate squeeze2raop config file in interactive mode
  - Added plugin commands and REST API
  - Added plugin settings view
  - Added registered device listing
  - Added device management (add/update/remove)
  - Evaluate server slimproto endpoint exposed to the plugin
  - POC to use squeeze2raop pre-built native executable in Python
